[h4 id=JumpReduction 
	" Jump Reduction
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"If you press buttons 1 or 2 mid jump at specific frames, Batman's jump will be reduced, this is beneficial since walking is faster than jumping.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"The button to press depends on the type of jump, if its the standard one, 1 should be pressed, which is the attack button, but if the jump is the drop kick, 2 should be pressed.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"The other jump kick can't be reduced.
	$LF
]div
