[div class=p 
	"The kind of jump you do depends on how close you are to an enemy, so many times its beneficial to turn around just before jumping to do a normal jump to jump over an enemy, instead of doing a jump attack, since that would push the enemy away and would have to be attacked again to clear him.
	$LF
]div
