[div class=p 
	"Batman's health comes in threes, so if you take three damage and lose one of the Batman icons, Batman dies, this is not the case in the autoscroller sections, where you can only die if you lose all your health, which is why one damage is taken in the helicopter section, so more damage can be taken in the last stage.
	$LF
